    Google BigQuery Table field. A table field has a name, a value, a mode and possibly a description. Supported types are: Field.Type.integer(), Field.Type.bool(), Field.Type.string(), Field.Type.floatingPoint(), Field.Type.timestamp() and Field.Type.record(Field...). One or more fields form a table's schema.
